##### Twitter Auto Follow How-To 

This template follows a specified acount

Follow these steps to test this template;

**1.** Edit the Config Node.

**2.** Update msg.twitter_account field with the account name which will be followed

**3.** Update msg.auth_token field with the auth_token cookie of your Twitter session. To obtain it follow the following steps:
   
       1. Login to your twitter account.
       2. Open developer options by 
          pressing F12
       3. Open Application tab
       4. Select cookies
       5. Copy auth_token cookie
          and paste it to msg.auth_token
          field in config node
